ss=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/theist\">theist</a>; <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of theo- \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/theo-\">theo-</a>; <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of theocracy \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/theocracy\">theocracy</a>; <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of theodicy \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/theodicy\">theodicy</a>; <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of Theodore \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/Theodore\">Theodore</a>; <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of Theodosia \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/Theodosia\">Theodosia</a>; <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of theogony \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/theogony\">theogony</a>; <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of theology \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/theology\">theology</a>; <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of theophany \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/theophany\">theophany</a>; <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of Theophilus \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/Theophilus\">Theophilus</a>; <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of theosophy \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/theosophy\">theosophy</a>; <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of theurgy \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/theurgy\">theurgy</a>; <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of tiffany \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/tiffany\">tiffany</a>; <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of Timothy \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/Timothy\">Timothy</a>。</p><p>它是以下单词的假设来源/其存在的证据由以下单词提供：希腊语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">theos</i> “神”； 拉丁语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">feriae</i> “假期